<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal" tal:omit-tag="textual">
<head tal:omit-tag="textual">
    <title tal:omit-tag="textual">Email address update on <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain name</span></title>
</head>
<body tal:omit-tag="textual">

    <h1 tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for confirming the update of your email address on the platform <span tal:replace="domain_name">Domain name</span></h1>
    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">You have asked us to change the email address that the <span tal:replace="domain_name">domain name</span> IT infrastructure will use to interact with you. To confirm your new email address please click on the confirmation link below.</p>
    <a tal:attributes="href string:${check_new_email_view}" tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <span tal:replace="string:${check_new_email_view}"></span>
    </a>

    <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Thank you for your interest in our activities.</p>
    
    <footer tal:omit-tag="textual">
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">Best regards,</p>
        <p tal:omit-tag="textual">The team at <span tal:replace="domain_name">Site</span></p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
